theorem toList_insertIdx (xs : Array α) (i x) (h) :
    (xs.insertIdx i x h).toList = xs.toList.insertIdx i x := by
  rcases xs with ⟨xs⟩
  simp
@[simp]
theorem insertIdx_zero (xs : Array α) (x : α) : xs.insertIdx 0 x = #[x] ++ xs := by
  rcases xs with ⟨xs⟩
  simp
@[simp] theorem size_insertIdx {xs : Array α}
